description:
On a hill far away in Calvary, there stood an old rugged cross, the emblem of suffering and shame. This is where Jesus was sentenced to die by crucifixion. Calvary was the lowest moment at the time for Jesus, but it turned out to be the highest moment in the history of the universe, providing hope to all.
